name: plataforma sensível/ sensory platform
description:
this is the second song of our first series, 'mambembe AI'.

'os_metasambas' makes language experiments w/ brazilian music and musical collages of stuff like glitchy sounds, funk carioca and electronic music.

@iagovrs
@danilomap

[letra:] 
metaversos de tatos, imagens
pirei de verdade (pirei de verdade)
e os mundos passando (passando)
e o cheiro da tua informação
seguro tua carne binária com gosto

[lyrics:]
metaverses, touch and image
I really freaked out (I really freaked out)
and the worlds passing by (passing by)
and the smell of your information
I hold your binary flesh with pleasure
